# Input

```scss
$mapValueScalar:(key:(value),);
$mapValueList:(key:(#d82d2d,#666),other-key:(#52bf4a,#fff),);
$mapValueMap:(key:(other-key:other-other-value),);
$mapValueScalarBroken:(key:(very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-scalar),);
$mapValueListBroken:(key:(very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-1,very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-2,very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-3),);
$mapValueMapBroken:(key:((very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-map-key:very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-map-value,other-key:other-other-value)),);

```


# Formatted

```scss
$mapValueScalar: (
	key: (value),
);
$mapValueList: (
	key: (#d82d2d, #666),
	other-key: (#52bf4a, #fff),
);
$mapValueMap: (
	key: (
		other-key: other-other-value,
	),
);
$mapValueScalarBroken: (
	key: (
		very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-scalar
	),
);
$mapValueListBroken: (
	key: (
			very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-1,
			very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-2,
			very-very-very-very-very-very-long-list-item-3,
	),
);
$mapValueMapBroken: (
	key: (
		(
			very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-map-key: very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-map-value,
			other-key: other-other-value,
		)
	),
);

```

